@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About";
}

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>About Fintrix - Fintrix</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8fafc 0%, #f1f5f9 100%);
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.5;
            color: #0f172a;
        }

        .about-container {
            max-width: 1280px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 2rem;
        }

        /* Hero Section */
        .hero-section {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 5rem;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.6s ease-out;
        }

        .hero-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.12);
            color: #2563eb;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            padding: 0.25rem 1rem;
            border-radius: 100px;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.3px;
        }

        .hero-title {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f2b3d 0%, #1e4a76 100%);
            background-clip: text;
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            color: transparent;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        }

        .hero-subtitle {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            color: #475569;
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .hero-image-wrapper {
            margin-top: 2.5rem;
            border-radius: 1.5rem;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
            background: #fff;
        }

            .hero-image-wrapper:hover {
                transform: translateY(-5px);
                box-shadow: 0 30px 60px -12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
            }

        .hero-image {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
            object-fit: cover;
            display: block;
            transition: transform 0.5s ease;
        }

        .hero-image-wrapper:hover .hero-image {
            transform: scale(1.02);
        }

        /* Cards Grid */
        .cards-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 4rem;
        }

        .info-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 1.5rem;
            padding: 2rem;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border: 1px solid rgba(226, 232, 240, 0.8);
        }

            .info-card:hover {
                transform: translateY(-6px);
                box-shadow: 0 20px 25px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
                border-color: #cbd5e1;
            }

        .card-icon {
            width: 52px;
            height: 52px;
            background: #eef2ff;
            border-radius: 1rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

            .card-icon svg {
                width: 28px;
                height: 28px;
                stroke: #2563eb;
                stroke-width: 1.7;
                fill: none;
            }

        .info-card h3 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
            color: #0f172a;
        }

        .info-card p {
            color: #334155;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* Mission & Vision Row */
        .mv-row {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 5rem;
        }

        .mv-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 1.5rem;
            padding: 2rem;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

            .mv-card:hover {
                box-shadow: 0 20px 25px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            }

            .mv-card h3 {
                font-size: 1.75rem;
                font-weight: 700;
                margin-bottom: 1rem;
                display: flex;
                align-items: center;
                gap: 0.75rem;
            }

                .mv-card h3 span {
                    font-size: 1.75rem;
                }

            .mv-card p {
                color: #334155;
                line-height: 1.7;
                font-size: 1.05rem;
            }

        /* Meet The Devs Section - Image on top, text below (Medium size - increased a bit from small) */
        .devs-section {
            margin-top: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }

        .devs-title {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            color: #0f172a;
            letter-spacing: -0.01em;
        }

        .devs-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(340px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        .dev-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 1.5rem;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            border: 1px solid #eef2ff;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

            .dev-card:hover {
                transform: translateY(-6px);
                box-shadow: 0 20px 30px -10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            }

        /* INCREASED IMAGE SIZE - medium/bigger than before, but still balanced */
        .dev-image {
            width: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(145deg, #f8fafc, #f1f5f9);
            overflow: hidden;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 2rem 2rem 1rem 2rem;
        }

            .dev-image img {
                width: 240px;
                height: 240px;
                object-fit: cover;
                object-position: center 20%;
                border-radius: 50%;
                display: block;
                transition: transform 0.4s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
                box-shadow: 0 15px 30px -10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
                border: 4px solid white;
            }

        .dev-card:hover .dev-image img {
            transform: scale(1.05);
            box-shadow: 0 25px 35px -12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
        }

        .dev-text {
            padding: 1.75rem 2rem 2rem 2rem;
            text-align: center;
        }

            .dev-text h3 {
                font-size: 1.5rem;
                font-weight: 700;
                margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
                color: #0f172a;
                line-height: 1.3;
            }

            .dev-text .dev-role {
                font-size: 0.9rem;
                color: #2563eb;
                font-weight: 600;
                margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
                letter-spacing: 0.3px;
                background: #eef2ff;
                display: inline-block;
                padding: 0.3rem 1rem;
                border-radius: 40px;
            }

            .dev-text p {
                color: #334155;
                line-height: 1.65;
                margin-bottom: 0.85rem;
                font-size: 0.95rem;
                text-align: left;
            }

        /* Stats Banner */
        .stats-banner {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a 0%, #1e293b 100%);
            border-radius: 2rem;
            padding: 3rem 2rem;
            margin: 3rem 0 2rem;
            color: white;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .stat-item h4 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff, #94a3b8);
            background-clip: text;
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            color: transparent;
        }

        .stat-item p {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #cbd5e1;
        }

        /* Animations */
        @@keyframes fadeInUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(24px);
            }

            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        .fade-up {
            animation: fadeInUp 0.6s ease-out forwards;
            opacity: 0;
        }

        .delay-1 {
            animation-delay: 0.1s;
        }

        .delay-2 {
            animation-delay: 0.2s;
        }

        .delay-3 {
            animation-delay: 0.3s;
        }

        .delay-4 {
            animation-delay: 0.4s;
        }

        /* Responsive adjustments for medium images */
        @@media (max-width: 768px) {
            .about-container {
                padding: 1rem;
            }

            .hero-title {
                font-size: 2.2rem;
            }

            .hero-subtitle {
                font-size: 1rem;
                padding: 0 1rem;
            }

            .mv-row {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 1.5rem;
            }

            .devs-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 1.5rem;
            }

            .dev-image img {
                width: 200px;
                height: 200px;
            }

            .dev-image {
                padding: 1.5rem 1.5rem 0.75rem 1.5rem;
            }

            .dev-text {
                padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem 1.5rem 1.5rem;
            }

                .dev-text h3 {
                    font-size: 1.35rem;
                }
        }

        @@media (max-width: 480px) {
            .hero-title {
                font-size: 1.8rem;
            }

            .devs-title {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }

            .mv-card h3 {
                font-size: 1.4rem;
            }

            .dev-image img {
                width: 160px;
                height: 160px;
            }

            .dev-image {
                padding: 1.25rem 1.25rem 0.5rem 1.25rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="about-container">
        <!-- Hero Section -->
        <div class="hero-section fade-up">
            <div class="hero-badge">Welcome to Fintrix</div>
            <h1 class="hero-title">Financial clarity,<br>redefined for you.</h1>
            <p class="hero-subtitle">Smart invoicing, real-time payments tracking, and total control over your cash flow — built for modern businesses and freelancers.</p>
            <div class="hero-image-wrapper">
                <img class="hero-image" src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/7869003/pexels-photo-7869003.jpeg"
                     alt="Fintrix Dashboard showing analytics and invoices" />
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Who We Are + Goal -->
        <div class="cards-grid">
            <div class="info-card fade-up delay-1">
                <div class="card-icon">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <path d="M20 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H8a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2" />
                        <circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4" />
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3>Who We Are</h3>
                <p>Fintrix is a modern fintech platform designed for businesses and freelancers who want complete control over their invoices, payments, and client financial interactions. Track paid, pending, and overdue invoices — all in one intelligent dashboard.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="info-card fade-up delay-2">
                <div class="card-icon">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" fill="none">
                        <path d="M12 2v4M12 18v4M4.93 4.93l2.83 2.83M16.24 16.24l2.83 2.83M2 12h4M18 12h4M4.93 19.07l2.83-2.83M16.24 7.76l2.83-2.83" />
                        <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3" />
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3>Our Goal</h3>
                <p>Simplify financial management for small businesses and freelancers. Provide real-time insights into client payments and outstanding invoices — helping you stay organized, save hours of manual work, and dramatically improve cash flow.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Mission & Vision -->
        <div class="mv-row">
            <div class="mv-card fade-up delay-3">
                <h3><span>🎯</span> Mission</h3>
                <p>Our mission is to empower businesses with tools that make tracking invoices, monitoring client payments, and managing finances intuitive and efficient. We reduce financial stress and give users absolute confidence in their cash flow management — so you can focus on growing your business, not chasing payments.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="mv-card fade-up delay-4">
                <h3><span>🔭</span> Vision</h3>
                <p>We envision a world where financial clarity is accessible to every business owner and freelancer. Fintrix aspires to be the go-to platform for smart, transparent, and reliable financial tracking — helping users build trust with clients and grow their business with confidence, anywhere in the world.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Meet The Devs - Medium sized images (240px) balanced and professional -->
        <div class="devs-section">
            <h2 class="devs-title">Meet The Devs</h2>

            <div class="devs-grid">
                <!-- Dev 1 - Philani: increased size to 240px width/height (medium) -->
                <div class="dev-card fade-up">
                    <div class="dev-image">
                        <img src="https://philani-khumalo-portfolio-main.vercel.app/assets/img7-CW-Cvrha.jpeg"
                             alt="Nhlakanipho Philani Khumalo - Backend Developer" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="dev-text">
                        <h3>Nhlakanipho Philani Khumalo</h3>
                        <div class="dev-role">Full-Stack Developer (Backend Focus)</div>
                        <p>I designed and developed the backend of this Smart Invoice & Payment System using ASP.NET Core. I built secure RESTful APIs with JWT authentication and structured the database using Entity Framework Core, ensuring proper relationships between users, clients, invoices, and payments.</p>
                        <p>I implemented business logic for invoice calculations and payment tracking with automatic status updates, and focused on designing clean API endpoints that integrate smoothly with the frontend, making it easy to display dashboards, invoices, and payments.</p>
                        <p>This project highlights my passion for building reliable and efficient backend systems.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Dev 2 - Mabel: increased image size (240px) for consistency, using a professional developer portrait -->
                <div class="dev-card fade-up">
                    <div class="dev-image">
                        <img src="~/image/mabel.jpg"
                             alt="Mabel Nwobi - Frontend Developer & UI/UX Designer" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="dev-text">
                        <h3>Mabel Nwobi</h3>
                        <div class="dev-role">Full-Stack Developer & UI/UX Designer</div>
                        <p>I developed the frontend of the application and was responsible for the complete UI/UX design using Figma, including wireframes and interactive prototypes. I also created the full brand identity, designing the logo and visual elements using Canva Pro.</p>
                        <p>I focused on building a responsive, intuitive, and user-centered interface, ensuring consistency between design and functionality. Every component is crafted to deliver a seamless experience across all devices.</p>
                        <p>This project demonstrates my ability to integrate frontend development, UI/UX design, and branding to deliver a polished and professional digital product.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Stats Banner for professional touch -->
        
    </div>
</body>
</html>